    <description>&gt;# [color=stublue]The Brewer[/color]
&gt;### Blue Dragon Offensive
&gt;**I Know My Wine (Passive) -** You are immune to poisonings and you will know if your target is poisoned or not. You keep this passive even if your class changes.
**Toast the Court (Passive) -** If you are executed on trial, you will cure all players of poisoning.
**Ale (Day ability) -** Poison a player. They will die in two nights if not healed - 2 uses.
**Party (Night) -** Occupy a player, preventing their night action - Infinite Uses.
**Sobriety (Night) -** Quietly make a player occupy and redirect immune for tonight - Infinite Uses.

**Converts to the [color=darkred]Invoker[/color] or the [color=purple]Poisoner[/color]**
&gt;# [color=Purple]The Poisoner[/color]
&gt;### Unseen Offensive (converted from Brewer)
&gt;**I Know My Wine (Passive) -** You are immune to poisonings and you will know if your target is poisoned or not. You keep this passive even if your class changes.
**Wine and Ale (Passive) -** If you are executed on trial, all member says of the Unseen will be immune to poisoning for tonight, as well as cured. A random Blue Dragon - never the king or any unique class — will be poisoned. They will die in two nights unless healed.
**Take a Break (Day ability) -** Prevent a player from using any day abilities for the rest of the day - 2 uses.
**Barrel of Mead (Night) -** Occupy a player for tonight - 3 uses.
**Sobriety (Night) -** Quietly make a player occupy and redirect immune. Can target Unseen - Infinite Uses.</description>
    
