        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Magnus]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <blockquote>
<h1><font color="stublue">The Brewer</font></h1>
<h3>Blue Dragon Offensive</h3>
<p><strong>I Know My Wine (Passive) -</strong> You are immune to poisonings and you will know if your target is poisoned or not. You keep this passive even if your class changes.<br>
<strong>Toast the Court (Passive) -</strong> If you are executed on trial, you will cure all players of poisoning.<br>
<strong>Ale (Day ability) -</strong> Poison a player. They will die in two nights if not healed - 2 uses.<br>
<strong>Party (Night) -</strong> Occupy a player, preventing their night action - Infinite Uses.<br>
<strong>Sobriety (Night) -</strong> Quietly make a player occupy and redirect immune for tonight - Infinite Uses.</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Converts to the <font color="darkred">Invoker</font> or the <font color="purple">Poisoner</font></strong></p>
<blockquote>
<h1><font color="Purple">The Poisoner</font></h1>
<h3>Unseen Offensive (converted from Brewer)</h3>
<p><strong>I Know My Wine (Passive) -</strong> You are immune to poisonings and you will know if your target is poisoned or not. You keep this passive even if your class changes.<br>
<strong>Wine and Ale (Passive) -</strong> If you are executed on trial, all member says of the Unseen will be immune to poisoning for tonight, as well as cured. A random Blue Dragon - never the king or any unique class — will be poisoned. They will die in two nights unless healed.<br>
<strong>Take a Break (Day ability) -</strong> Prevent a player from using any day abilities for the rest of the day - 2 uses.<br>
<strong>Barrel of Mead (Night) -</strong> Occupy a player for tonight - 3 uses.<br>
<strong>Sobriety (Night) -</strong> Quietly make a player occupy and redirect immune. Can target Unseen - Infinite Uses.</p>
</blockquote>
